crimes of their fathers but we do demand nonetheless an 
admission of collective responsibility 
in an address to the delegates kohl said never may it be 
forgotten that the genocide of the european jews was prepared and 
directed by the national socialists nazis under the violent 
leadership from berlin 
he said it remained the duty of all democratic powers also 
those in a united germany to fight without compromise against 
those who secretly or openly spread prejudice 
