brought to 110000 pounds the amount of cocaine seized by security 
forces in the last 16 months authorities said 
they began thursday ended saturday and netted 26400 pounds of 
the drug they said the previous colombian record was 22000 
pounds or 11 tons found in remote southern colombia six years ago 
