they immediately became popular destinations for backpackers 
traveling overland from nepal and for package tours flying in from 
the chinese city of chengdu 
about 30000 tourists visited tibet in 1986 the last year 
unmarred by bloody clashes between tibetan nationalists and chinese 
security forces 
china says its sovereignty over tibet dates to the 13th century 
tibetan nationalists say the region was actually independent much 
of that time and should be now 
