building when mondays session opened they unfurled a red banner 
reading comrades have no doubt we will defend the interests of 
the ussr with honor thousands of soviet troops are stationed 
in latvia 
latvians incensed by the slogans ominous tone shouted 
shame in russian at the soldiers the argument remained 
peaceful 
