residents of the mostly white neighborhood who saw much or all of 
the attack but refused to come forward 
he spoke of the door stoops where the brother and sisterhood 
of bensonhurst sat watching but not seeing hearing but not 
listening as hawkins was surrounded by a white mob and shot 
through the chest 
