vere c bird jr public works minister and national security 
adviser to his father antiguan prime minister vere bird has been 
implicated in the case the younger bird denied wrongdoing but 
stepped down until the issue is resolved 
in april 1989 israel delivered to the antiguan government 100 
uzi submachine guns with short barrels 400 galil automatic assault 
rifles and matching ammunition an israeli official said speaking 
on condition of anonymity 
the shipment ended up at the ranch of gonzalo rodriguez gacha a 
notorious drug lord who died last december in a shootout with 
colombian police 
after colombian officials discovered the cache they approached 
israel with serial numbers from 200 galils made by israel military 
industries a defense ministry statement said monday 
it said the serial numbers were found to match the numbers of 
the rifles belonging to the shipment delivered to the antiguan 
government 
