presented a letter introducing himself as an official envoy of 
antiguas foreign ministry published reports said sarfati is a 
former israeli army officer 
we received a receipt from the government customs agent in 
antigua that they had received the shipment we had no idea that 
anything went wrong for almost a year bina said 
then we got a message from the antiguan government asking for 
the details of who made the order and who received it they said 
the government did not order it he said 
sarfati presented to israeli authorities an order for the 
shipment an end user certificate guaranteeing the arms would be 
for sole use of the antiguan army and his accreditation letter 
from the antiguan government 
