to 30 million had pleaded guilty to one count of wire fraud 
other counts involving federal bank insurance fraud and 
racketeering conspiracy were dropped as part of the deal 
the sentence giving the philippines total control of the bank 
was a victory for president corazon aquinos government which 
seeks to recover more than 220 million allegedly embezzled by the 
marcoses from the countrys treasury during marcos 20 years in 
power 
