the first wouldbe prek parent arrived at 530 pm the evening 
before registration someone soon arrived with numbers to pass out 
there was a signin sheet too just as a backstop 
my husband manny schiffres and i stopped at the school at 815 
pm as we were returning from a reception eight people were there 
we drove the three blocks to our house when we got there the 
phone was ringing and a notice was posted near the telephone get 
over to lafayette people are already there it was signed by my 
nextdoor neighbor and timed off at 730 
i changed my clothes putting on a 20yearold sweater and a 
pair of jeans my neighbor rang the bell come on we have to 
go she said grabbing a down jacket and a cup of cherry yogurt 
i returned to the school with her 
i was number 16 rebecca was in 
people milled around the courtyard spouses came with dinner and 
with kids to say goodnight a table with wine and cheese was set up 
under a newly posted sign warning that no alcohol or drugs was 
permitted within 1000 feet of the school 
