and additional provisions for future cleanup costs this year 
helped depress its latest results 
for the first three months of 1990 arco netted 547 million or 
328 per share down from earnings of 704 million or 4 a share 
in 1989 sales were up 6 percent to 421 billion from 396 
billion 
